---
import { site } from "../site.config";
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Why hire a solo contractor over an agency.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">
        {/* TODO: this is a starting draft — rewrite in your own voice / add a real bio + photo. */}
        I'm {site.ownerName}, and {site.name} is how I take on contract and
        freelance work outside a day job spent building production React,
        TypeScript, and Flutter apps. Every project on this page is something
        I designed, built, and shipped alone — front to back — which is the
        same way I work with clients: one person who owns the whole problem,
        not a hand-off between three specialists.
      </p>
      <p class="section-lede">
        That means faster iteration, fewer meetings, and code you can hand to
        your own team afterward without a translation layer.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul class="stats">
      <li><strong>3+</strong><span>shipped side projects, all live in this portfolio</span></li>
      <li><strong>2</strong><span>platforms per project on average — mobile, web, and desktop from one codebase</span></li>
      <li><strong>0</strong><span>hand-offs — one person designs, builds, and ships</span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 56px;
  }

  .stats {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 26px;
    align-self: center;
  }

  .stats li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-left: 18px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .stats strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .stats span {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
